  "book.netherman.page1.line1": "欢迎来到 §4§lCult of Azazel§f§l 模组！",
  "book.netherman.page1.line2": "这是本模组的快速指南。",
  "book.netherman.page1.line3": "感谢游玩！",
  "book.netherman.page1.line4": "作者：§4Benj1kus",
  "book.netherman.page1.line5": "§c§l介绍：",
  "book.netherman.page1.line6": "本模组为游戏添加了新的结构，",
  "book.netherman.page1.line7": "主要围绕下界展开。",

  "book.netherman.page2.line1": "§c§l结构：§4§l下界宅邸",
  "book.netherman.page2.line2": "这是一座被分为3个区域的巨大宅邸：",
  "book.netherman.page2.line3": "§6§l被诅咒的采石场",
  "book.netherman.page2.line4": "§c§l神圣之城",
  "book.netherman.page2.line5": "§4§l阿撒泻勒之巢",
  "book.netherman.page2.line6": "§6§l被诅咒的采石场：§f§l起始区域",
  "book.netherman.page2.line7": "玩家将在此遇到§4操纵者。",
  "book.netherman.page2.line8": "击败他们后可以解救村民",
  "book.netherman.page2.line9": "并获得奖励。",

  "book.netherman.page3.line1": "§c§l神圣之城：§f§l第二区域",
  "book.netherman.page3.line2": "这里主要用于探索。",
  "book.netherman.page3.line3": "你可以找到2位NPC：",
  "book.netherman.page3.line4": "§c医生§f§l - 可给予随机药水",
  "book.netherman.page3.line5": "§c铁匠§f§l - 可拆解和修理工具",
  "book.netherman.page3.line6": "且不会移除附魔。",
  "book.netherman.page3.line7": "§4§l阿撒泻勒之巢：§f§l最终区域",
  "book.netherman.page3.line8": "木桶中有一份说明书",
  "book.netherman.page3.line9": "讲解如何召唤§4§l阿撒泻勒。",

  "book.netherman.page4.line1": "§c§l下界小型结构",
  "book.netherman.page4.line2": "§2§l主世界结构",
  "book.netherman.page4.line3": "在地表有时可以看见",
  "book.netherman.page4.line4": "喷出熔岩间歇泉的管道。",
  "book.netherman.page4.line5": "其下方是下界裂隙，",
  "book.netherman.page4.line6": "需要在那里获取指南针钥匙，",
  "book.netherman.page4.line7": "它将指引你前往 ???",

  "book.netherman.page5.line1": "§c§l生物：§4Ghastly",
  "book.netherman.page5.line2": "可用绯红菌柄建造蜂巢，",
  "book.netherman.page5.line3": "能够生产绯红蜂蜜，",
  "book.netherman.page5.line4": "可以被驯服，",
  "book.netherman.page5.line5": "能够指引下界宅邸的位置。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line6": "§c§l次要生物：",
  "book.netherman.page5.line7": "§6Welcomer§f§l - 在入口欢迎玩家。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line8": "§6Trader§f§l - 提供各种交易。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line9": "§6镀金傀儡§f§l - 保护信徒，吸收物品与鲜血。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line10": "§4Gehinnom§f§l - 守卫，最好不要招惹。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line11": "§4Manipulator§f§l - 阿撒泻勒的仆从，负责资源管理。",

  "book.netherman.page6.line1": "§c§l物品",
  "book.netherman.page6.line2": "§c重生图腾：",
  "book.netherman.page6.line3": "受到致命伤害时会传送至重生点。",
  "book.netherman.page6.line4": "§4操纵法杖：",
  "book.netherman.page6.line5": "可施加操纵效果，",
  "book.netherman.page6.line6": "拉拽实体并召唤凋灵骷髅。",
  "book.netherman.page6.line7": "§e§l感谢游玩！",
  "book.netherman.page6.line8": "作者：§4Benj1kus",

